reviewText: I literally cried while watching this. This is definitely something I'll never get tired of watching. All the songs are great and all the girls are beautiful. This is one of my favorites. Taeyeon looks so gorgeous and her voice just kills me. I highly recommend you get this, just make you have some tissues with you before you watch it. GG Fighting!!!:)

This is the culmination of 4 Japanese tours, & this one highlights & improves upon the sequences of songs & movies with medley sections like a mix CD & also has quite emotional moments. It is No. 2 to me, No. 1 being the 3rd Japanese tour, but this one is necessary, exciting & unbelievable to view again & again! I could write about this for hours, but you just need to order it & see for yourself & your friends!  A++
